original_title: 我才不信你是个王子呢
overview: It tells the story of Illidan's king Malfurion Karimdor Kil'jaeden and ordinary high school student Lu Hani, from accidentally meeting to becoming friends, the gap between the two people's life experience from childhood to old age. adult. There were many contradictions between them.
title: I Don't Believe You're a Prince
